Class InitializeTableFromTextFile

java.lang.Object
org.tensorflow.op.RawOp
org.tensorflow.op.core.InitializeTableFromTextFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Op
@Operator public final class InitializeTableFromTextFile extends RawOp
Initializes a table from a text file. It inserts one key-value pair into the table for each line of the file. The key and value is extracted from the whole line content, elements from the split line based on delimiter or the line number (starting from zero). Where to extract the key and value from a line is specified by key_index and value_index.
  • A value of -1 means use the line number(starting from zero), expects int64.
  • A value of -2 means use the whole line content, expects string.
  • A value >= 0 means use the index (starting at zero) of the split line based on delimiter.
